Version: 1.2.0 - 2007-03-22
===========================

- Added new function handleSIGCLD/restoreSIGCLD for setting
  up/removing a SIGCLD handler so that fork'ed processes can safely be
  ignored without becoming zombies.  See ?handleSIGCLD for details.  

- Added regression tests for SysV and BSD style signal handling that
  checks for zombie process creation & tests that signal("SIGCHLD","ignore")
  and/or handleSIGCLD() prevents zombie process creation.
    
